# NovaMLM Software — Cursor & AI Rules (Dark Black Theme Lock)

Strictly enforce rules from Brand Guidelines.pdf and DESIGN_SYSTEM_RULES.md:

- Font: Use Figtree ONLY across all elements (headlines, body, nav, badges, numbers).
- Page Background: #08070B (Sleek Dark Shade of Black)
- Card Surface: #121017 (--navy-card / --charcoal)
- Primary Accent: #0090FF / #1164F0 (--blue-vibrant / --nova)
- Highlight Cyan: #5EEBFC (--cyan-light / --moss)
- Primary Text: #FFFFFF (--white / --bone)
- Secondary Text: #A19CBB (--smoke-blue / --smoke)
- Logo: Official geometric 'N' block brandmark + NovaMLM Software lockup.
